{"tid":294212,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我沒有運氣放大自私的失意","createTime":"2017-06-22T18:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T19:55:50.000Z","uid":5459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc044c10030692c3d21b0048fc64c0cfeebe5a7","tid":294212,"uid":5459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:10:22.000Z","msg":"一諗起佢同新對象曖曖昧昧就萬箭穿心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偏偏日日都會見到佢<br />\n每次見佢都要特登同佢保持返朋友應有嘅距離<br />\n聽佢講佢同佢而家個曖昧對象點點點我仲要笑住畀建議佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但嗰刻我心入面已經乸埋一嚿<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明佢冇可能鍾意我，點解我認清咗呢個事實都死唔到心<br />\n我真係冇辦法令自己停止鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底仲要捱幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517c1da1701cf036a63cffb2999307fe6d48a6a2","tid":294212,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:15:29.000Z","msg":"睇開啲啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fb5371af16922943c41528f90e7dc05c86a2d8","tid":294212,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"良心可一敲即碎 女人開始使我恐懼"},{"pid":"a5b2b320585eb08a3caa4ec175067b04fe10dda3","tid":294212,"uid":66699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T1